This paper discusses the vulnerability of deep neural networks to adversarial examples and the research progress in generating and defending against them. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
